snippet.title: Paranoia 2 Savior Official Trailer #1
snippet.description: The Paranoia 2: Savior (P2S) is a free-to-play Action/FPS/Horror PC game for Windows OS based on «Xash3D» engine. It’s a sequel to 2008s «PARANOIA» mod which was itself based on GoldSrc engine. The «P2S» grew so big that it became a standalone game, and is no longer considered a mod.
